Royal Deer
The governor is very keen to own a golden nugget. You can get one from the Royal Deer's dead body.
#subobj  1
Deer valley
The Royal Deer lives in the big valley north of the river connecting the two lakes.
#subobj  2
Finding Royal Deer
The Royal Deer looks no different from any other deer. But unlike the others,  he is capable of defending himself.
#subobj  3
Killing the Royal Deer
The only way to get the golden nugget is to kill the Royal Deer.
#subobj  4
Taking the nugget
Take the nugget from the Deer's dead body.
